<i>are suspected of illegal involvement</i>

522
00:40:12,493 --> 00:40:14,078
[Ondam Hotel: The "Entertainment" Protocol]
<i>with aspiring entertainers.</i>

523
00:40:14,078 --> 00:40:17,030
<i>They intend to widen the investigation.</i>

524
00:40:17,030 --> 00:40:22,170
<i>Mr. Nam, who was locked up last April
for the murder of rookie actress Ms. Hwang,</i>

525
00:40:22,170 --> 00:40:26,640
<i>has been cleared of all charges
and walked free this morning after ten months.</i>

526
00:41:40,248 --> 00:41:43,500
Petit! Petit! Petit!

527
00:41:43,500 --> 00:41:46,553
My man, Tae Seop!

528
00:41:48,042 --> 00:41:51,225
